description:
On a brand new Unqualified, Anna and Sim talk to actor/musician Nick Jonas (JUMANJI: WELCOME TO THE JUNGLE, CHAOS WALKING, HOME) about being nominated for a Golden Globe (2:40), not having an ego about fame (4:40), and his ideal relationship (10:35). Then they play a round of Deal Breakers (13:30) and How Would You Proceed? (20:10)

After the break, they play a new game called What's Your Mood? (34:00) and take a call from Samantha, who's suspicious of her boyfriend's relationship with his ex girlfriend who's trying to shut Samantha out of their friend group. (43:28)
